    <item>
      <title>随着量化宽松政策的结束，新西兰央行资产负债表缩减至 2021 年以来的最低水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/rbnz-balance-sheet-shrinks-to-smallest-since-2021-as-qe-unwinds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着新西兰央行继续减少其在疫情期间购买的债券持有量，其资产负债表规模已缩减至三年多以来的最小规模。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/rbnz-balance-sheet-shrinks-to-smallest-since-2021-as-qe-unwinds</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Sep 2024 04:00:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
